<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Feature Engineering — Herramienta Interactiva</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;600&family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,300;0,700;0,900;1,300&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #f0f2f8;
  --surface: #ffffff;
  --surface2: #f5f6fb;
  --surface3: #eceef6;
  --border: #d4d8ee;
  --border2: #e0e3f0;
  --g1: #0fa37a;
  --g2: #5b4fcf;
  --g3: #d4700a;
  --g4: #c4317a;
  --g5: #0b8fc4;
  --g6: #5a8a00;
  --text: #1a1c2e;
  --muted: #6b6f94;
  --muted2: #a0a4c0;
  --danger: #d93030;
  --warn: #b07800;
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* TOPBAR */
.topbar {
  position: sticky; top:0; z-index:100;
  background: rgba(240,242,248,0.95);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0;
  padding: 0 28px;
  height: 52px;
  overflow-x: auto;
}

.topbar-brand {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 17px;
  color: var(--g1);
  margin-right: 28px;
  white-space: nowrap;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.nav-btn {
  background: none; border: none;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11.5px;
  color: var(--muted);
  padding: 0 14px;
  height: 52px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: color 0.2s, border-bottom 0.2s;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  white-space: nowrap;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.nav-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }
.nav-btn.active { color: var(--g1); border-bottom-color: var(--g1); }

/* HERO */
.hero {
  padding: 60px 40px 40px;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--g1);
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 68px);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.0;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.hero-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--g2);
}

.hero-sub {
  font-size: 17px;
  color: var(--muted);
  max-width: 640px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.hero-stats {
  display: flex; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.stat {
  text-align: left;
}

.stat-num {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--g1);
  line-height: 1;
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

/* MAIN */
.main { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 80px; }

/* SECTION */
.section {
  display: none;
}
.section.visible { display: block; }

/* MODULE CARD */
.module {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
}

.module:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }

.module-header {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 22px 24px;
  cursor: pointer;
  user-select: none;
}

.module-header:hover .module-title { color: var(--g1); }

.module-icon {
  width: 42px; height: 42px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 18px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.module-title {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: 21px;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}

.module-subtitle {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  margin-top: 3px;
}

.module-chevron {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--muted);
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.module.open .module-chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }

.module-body {
  display: none;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--surface);
}

.module.open .module-body { display: block; }

/* TABS INSIDE MODULE */
.module-tabs {
  display: flex;
  padding: 0 24px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  gap: 4px;
  overflow-x: auto;
}

.mtab {
  background: none; border: none;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11.5px;
  color: var(--muted);
  padding: 12px 14px;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  white-space: nowrap;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.mtab.active { color: var(--text); border-bottom-color: var(--accent-color, var(--g1)); }
.mtab:hover { color: var(--text); }

/* TAB PANELS */
.mpanel { display: none; padding: 24px; }
.mpanel.active { display: grid; gap: 20px; }

/* TWO-COL */
.two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
.three-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
.one-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .two-col, .three-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

/* EXPLANATION BOX */
.explain {
  background: var(--surface2);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 18px;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-color, var(--g1));
}

.explain-title {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--accent-color, var(--g1));
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.explain p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.explain p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.explain strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

/* CANVAS CHART */
.chart-wrap {
  background: var(--surface2);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 16px;
  position: relative;
}

.chart-label {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

canvas {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 6px;
}

/* CONTROLS */
.controls {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.ctrl-label {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.ctrl-btn {
  background: var(--surface3);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.ctrl-btn:hover, .ctrl-btn.active {
  background: var(--accent-color, var(--g1));
  color: #000;
  border-color: var(--accent-color, var(--g1));
}

input[type=range] {
  accent-color: var(--accent-color, var(--g1));
  height: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* CODE BOX */
.code-box {
  background: #f0f4ff;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12.5px;
  color: #3a3d6a;
  line-height: 1.9;
  overflow-x: auto;
  white-space: pre;
}

.code-box .kw { color: var(--g2); }
.code-box .fn { color: var(--g1); }
.code-box .st { color: var(--g3); }
.code-box .cm { color: var(--muted2); }
.code-box .num { color: var(--g4); }

/* WHEN-WHY BOX */
.when-why {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 12px;
}

.ww-card {
  background: var(--surface3);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 14px;
  border-top: 2px solid;
}

.ww-card.when { border-color: var(--g5); }
.ww-card.why { border-color: var(--g6); }
.ww-card.avoid { border-color: var(--danger); }
.ww-card.example { border-color: var(--g3); }

.ww-title {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.ww-card.when .ww-title { color: var(--g5); }
.ww-card.why .ww-title { color: var(--g6); }
.ww-card.avoid .ww-title { color: var(--danger); }
.ww-card.example .ww-title { color: var(--g3); }

.ww-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
.ww-card ul li {
  font-size: 13.5px;
  color: var(--muted);
  padding: 3px 0 3px 14px;
  position: relative;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.ww-card ul li::before { content: '—'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--muted2); }

/* FULLWIDTH */
.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }

/* BADGE */
.badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  border: 1px solid currentColor;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  margin: 2px;
}

/* TABLE */
.nice-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 13px;
}

.nice-table th {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  padding: 10px 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  text-align: left;
}

.nice-table td {
  padding: 10px 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2);
  color: var(--muted);
  vertical-align: top;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.nice-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.nice-table .hl { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
.nice-table .yes { color: var(--g1); }
.nice-table .no { color: var(--danger); }
.nice-table .partial { color: var(--warn); }

/* INTERACTIVE DEMO */
.demo-area {
  background: var(--surface2);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 18px;
}

.demo-title {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

/* LEAKAGE DEMO */
.leak-timeline {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0;
  margin: 16px 0;
}

.lt-block {
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 10px 12px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  text-align: center;
  flex: 1;
}

.lt-arrow { color: var(--muted2); font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; padding: 0 4px; }

/* SKEW INDICATOR */
.skew-bar {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 12px;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

.skew-fill {
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background: var(--accent-color, var(--g1));
  transition: width 0.5s;
}

/* SECTION HEADING */
.sec-heading {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-size: 30px;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  margin-top: 40px;
}

.sec-sub {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

/* PROGRESS BAR */
.progress-bar {
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--border);
  border-radius: 2px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin: 8px 0;
}
.progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: width 1s ease;
}

/* COMPARISON VISUAL */
.comparison {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}

.comp-arrow {
  font-size: 24px;
  color: var(--accent-color, var(--g1));
  text-align: center;
}

.comp-box {
  background: var(--surface3);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 14px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.comp-box-title {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

/* TOOLTIP */
.tooltip {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  cursor: help;
  border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--muted2);
}

.tooltip:hover::after {
  content: attr(data-tip);
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 125%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background: var(--surface3);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text);
  padding: 6px 10px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-size: 11px;
  white-space: nowrap;
  z-index: 100;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* SLIDER DEMO */
.slider-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin: 8px 0;
  font-size: 13px;
}

.slider-row label {
  width: 120px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
}

.slider-val {
  width: 50px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--accent-color, var(--g1));
  text-align: right;
}

/* Scrollbar */
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--muted2); border-radius: 3px; }

/* ALERT BOX */
.alert {
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  border-left: 3px solid;
}

.alert.danger { background: #fff0f0; border-color: var(--danger); color: #9b3030; }
.alert.warning { background: #fffbf0; border-color: var(--warn); color: #7a5a00; }
.alert.info { background: #f0f6ff; border-color: var(--g5); color: #1e6090; }
.alert strong { color: var(--text); }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOPBAR -->
<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-brand">⟁ FeatEng</div>
  <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="showSection('overview', this)">INICIO</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('numerical', this)">NUMÉRICAS</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('categorical', this)">CATEGÓRICAS</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('temporal', this)">TEMPORALES</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('selection', this)">SELECCIÓN</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('scaling', this)">ESCALADO</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showSection('leakage', this)">LEAKAGE</button>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">// HERRAMIENTA INTERACTIVA · CIENCIAS DE DATOS · ML</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">Feature<br><em>Engineering</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Aprende cuándo, por qué y cómo transformar datos crudos en señales poderosas para tus modelos. Cada concepto incluye visualizaciones interactivas y ejemplos reales.</p>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">8</div><div class="stat-label">Módulos</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">20+</div><div class="stat-label">Técnicas</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">∞</div><div class="stat-label">Visualizaciones vivas</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="main">

<!-- =================== OVERVIEW =================== -->
<div class="section visible" id="sec-overview">

  <div class="sec-heading">¿Por qué Feature Engineering?</div>
  <div class="sec-sub">// La intuición fundamental antes de ver las técnicas</div>

  <!-- WHY BLOCK -->
  <div class="module" style="--accent-color: var(--g1);" id="mod-why">
    <div class="module-header" onclick="toggleModule('mod-why')">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#e6f7f2;">🎯</div>
      <div>
        <div class="module-title">El principio fundamental</div>
        <div class="module-subtitle">GARBAGE IN → GARBAGE OUT · Los modelos no crean información, la amplifican</div>
      </div>
      <div class="module-chevron">▾</div>
    </div>
    <div class="module-body">
      <div class="module-tabs" style="--accent-color:var(--g1)">
        <button class="mtab active" onclick="switchTab(this,'why-t1')">CONCEPTO</button>
        <button class="mtab" onclick="switchTab(this,'why-t2')">DEMOSTRACIÓN</button>
        <button class="mtab" onclick="switchTab(this,'why-t3')">EJEMPLO REAL</button>
      </div>

      <div class="mpanel active one-col" id="why-t1">
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px;">
          <div class="explain" style="--accent-color:var(--g1)">
            <div class="explain-title">¿Qué es Feature Engineering?</div>
            <p>Es el proceso de <strong>transformar datos crudos en representaciones</strong> que los algoritmos de Machine Learning puedan entender y aprovechar mejor.</p>
            <p>Un modelo de ML es básicamente una función matemática. Si le das señales pobres, aprenderá relaciones pobres. Si le das señales ricas, aprenderá relaciones poderosas.</p>
            <p><strong>Ejemplo:</strong> Un árbol de decisión no puede "ver" que "enero" y "diciembre" están cerca en el tiempo. Pero si creas sin(2π·mes/12), sí puede.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="explain" style="--accent-color:var(--g2)">
            <div class="explain-title">¿Cuándo es crítico?</div>
            <p>Siempre, pero especialmente cuando:</p>
            <p>• Los datos tienen <strong>distribuciones sesgadas</strong> (precios, salarios, clics)</p>
            <p>• Hay <strong>variables categóricas</strong> que el modelo no puede leer directamente</p>
            <p>• Tienes <strong>fechas o texto</strong> sin procesar</p>
            <p>• El modelo tiene <strong>bajo rendimiento</strong> pese a muchos datos</p>
            <p>• Hay <strong>relaciones no lineales</strong> entre variables</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--surface2); border-radius:10px; padding:18px;">
          <div class="demo-title">IMPACTO TÍPICO EN MÉTRICAS</div>
          <div id="impact-bars"></div>
          <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:12px; font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;">*Datos ilustrativos basados en casos reales reportados en competencias Kaggle y papers académicos.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mpanel one-col" id="why-t2">
        <div class="demo-area">
          <div class="demo-title">DEMO: PREDECIR PRECIO DE CASA — FEATURES CRUDAS vs ENGINEERED</div>
          <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; margin-bottom:16px;">
            <div>
              <div class="comp-box-title" style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:10px;">DATOS CRUDOS</div>
              <canvas id="raw-scatter" height="200"></canvas>
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;">R² ≈ 0.41 — Relación lineal débil</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="comp-box-title" style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--g1);letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:10px;">CON LOG TRANSFORM</div>
              <canvas id="log-scatter" height="200"></canvas>
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--g1);margin-top:8px;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;">R² ≈ 0.78 — Relación lineal fuerte ✓</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="alert info">
            <strong>¿Qué pasó?</strong> Los precios de casas siguen una distribución log-normal. Al aplicar log(), la relación con el área se vuelve lineal y la regresión lineal la puede capturar perfectamente.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mpanel one-col" id="why-t3">
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:14px;">
          <div class="ww-card example">
            <div class="ww-title">🏥 Medicina</div>
            <ul><li>IMC = peso/altura²</li><li>Cambio de presión sanguínea</li><li>Días desde último evento</li><li>Ratio LDL/HDL</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="ww-card example" style="border-color:var(--g2)">
            <div class="ww-title" style="color:var(--g2)">💳 Finanzas</div>
            <ul><li>Ratio deuda/ingreso</li><li>Volatilidad 30 días</li><li>Días sin transacciones</li><li>Cambio % mes anterior</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="ww-card example" style="border-color:var(--g5)">
            <div class="ww-title" style="color:var(--g5)">🛒 E-commerce</div>
            <ul><li>Tasa de conversión histórica</li><li>Días desde última compra</li><li>Categorías únicas compradas</li><li>Ticket promedio por sesión</li></ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="alert warning">
